\pard\pardeftab720\sl420\ql\qnatural\pardirnatural
\cf0 1. Whether the defendant is liable without the company Children Vision Uganda being sued. 
\f1 \uc0\u8232 
\f0 2. If the defendant is liable whether he is to pay the whole sum claimed as prayed.
\f1 \uc0\u8232 
\f0 3. Remedies.\
